  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbe \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The President announced his resignation",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardena has announced that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has announced his resignation from the presidency.",
        "Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardena has also announced that he will resign from the presidency on July 13th.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has agreed to resign as per the decision taken in the party leader's meeting.",
        "The Speaker also mentioned that he has informed the people of the country that he will announce his resignation on Wednesday the 13th, as he must hand over the power peacefully anyway."
      ],
